00:13:39,743 --> 00:13:42,263
when driving while having a conversation over the phone,

255
00:13:42,763 --> 00:13:45,204
it requires more cognitive load to process

256
00:13:45,244 --> 00:13:47,524
the different information, therefore leading

257
00:13:47,564 --> 00:13:48,865
to more fatigue and mistakes.

258
00:13:49,585 --> 00:13:51,345
The more demanding a specific task

259
00:13:52,226 --> 00:13:54,366
is in terms of cognitive load, for example,

260
00:13:54,586 --> 00:13:56,927
mental calculation, the less people

261
00:13:56,967 --> 00:13:59,187
can allocate mental effort to accomplish another task,

262
00:13:59,247 --> 00:14:01,228
even though simple, such as pressing a button

263
00:14:01,528 --> 00:14:02,728
when a red light goes off.

