00:15:55,293 --> 00:15:57,333
are using the same limited attentional resources,

300
00:15:57,893 --> 00:15:59,994
the developers must mind the cognitive load

301
00:16:00,654 --> 00:16:02,054
the game demands from the player,

302
00:16:02,414 --> 00:16:04,395
especially, again, during the onboarding part

