00:16:10,876 --> 00:16:13,277
So according to the cognitive load theory,

305
00:16:13,757 --> 00:16:16,278
learning can be hindered if it requires

306
00:16:16,338 --> 00:16:19,618
cognitive resources exceeding the working memory limits.

