00:17:13,987 --> 00:17:17,728
The first time he learns about a mechanic, it's going to require a lot of cognitive load.

321
00:17:18,428 --> 00:17:24,330
Later down the line, when the player really had that going, it's trained to doing it,

322
00:17:24,390 --> 00:17:27,472
it's more automated, it does not require as much cognitive load.

323
00:17:28,462 --> 00:17:31,103
So three items could be one, using an ability

