00:23:50,467 --> 00:23:53,728
So when you click on the plus button there to slot a worker,

452
00:23:54,228 --> 00:23:56,629
it was showing the workers you could slot,

453
00:23:57,089 --> 00:23:59,310
including the ones already slotted elsewhere.

454
00:23:59,890 --> 00:24:02,371
Suddenly indicated by that red corner mark.

455
00:24:03,151 --> 00:24:04,252
I'm sure you saw it, right?

456
00:24:05,172 --> 00:24:06,833
Of course players didn't see it.

457
00:24:07,393 --> 00:24:08,853
And on this video you're going to see,

458
00:24:09,794 --> 00:24:11,374
you'll see the player going back and forth

459
00:24:11,594 --> 00:24:13,955
in the two buildings trying to slot a worker,

