uh...

467
00:24:29,187 --> 00:24:35,672
so we have to pay attention to that

468
00:24:49,861 --> 00:24:55,125
Functional affordance, this is one that ties usage to usefulness.

469
00:24:55,785 --> 00:24:58,347
This is when you add a functionality, such as sorting

470
00:24:59,068 --> 00:25:01,249
and categories to help the player find something.

471
00:25:02,270 --> 00:25:05,532
Filtering, in that example you see, well, there's filtering,

